{{Infobox person
| name = Sir Anthony Hopkins
| image = Anthony Hopkins-Tuscan Sun Festival.jpg
| caption = Hopkins at the Tuscan Sun Festival, [[Cortona]], 2009
| birth_date = {{Birth date and age|df=yes|1937|12|31}}
