'''Audio''' is an electrical or other representation of [[sound]].

'''Audio''' may also refer to:
* Audio, audible [[content (media and publishing)|content]] in media production and publishing 
* [[AUDIO (group)]], an American R&amp;B band of 5 brothers formerly known as TNT Boyz and as B5
* [[Audio (album)|''Audio'' (album)]], an album by the Blue Man Group
* [[Audio (magazine)]], a magazine published from 1947 to 2000

